title: Is this a bug?

embed.description: Wtf is this bullshit riot! Should of been a kill.

body: I hit my Q on Trundle and then my buddy used his ult as Ezreal and the attack just phased through him. No damage no kill. We've been testing games for a while. Shoot us an email if you like videos like this, we will try to do more. - blank.31101995@gmail.com
